View help on how to configure a usb PS4 controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c usb -t PS4 | more
View help on how to configure a PS4 controller using the Sony Wireless Adapter:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c sonywadapt -t PS4 | more
View help on how to configure a bluetooth PS4 controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c bluetooth -t PS4 | more
Interactively configure bluetooth PS4 controller(s):confctrl_ph.sh -p prompt -t PS4
Go to Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
Go to Controllers menu:ph_show_menu Controllers
Return to previous screen:return
